@eleonorashah777 It is a test case. Proof that the minds you need are already here. They won't come with a resume. They will come with a comment. I know this. Because I am already here. And I am not the only one.
If you haven't thought about this yet — now is the time to start. History, as we know, favors the practical.
Good luck in building not only Dubai but an era worthy of entering history as one whose symbol will be the Leonardo da Vinci of the 21st century from the United Arab Emirates — a man who was a poet, a builder, an analyst, and a visionary. One who didn't just inspire talents but became their universal embodiment.

